Package: SLR.prediction.vis
Type: Package
Title: A quick and easy way of predicting within a simple linear regression model + visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Emanuel Sommer
Maintainer: Emanuel Sommer
Description: The package includes functions for quickly predicting specific values in a simple linear regression framework. It also provides a visualization function that draws a scatterplot of the data, the regression line and the highlights the prediction.
